@startuml Sequence_Admin_ContentModeration
title Quản Trị - Duyệt Nội Dung

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant ModerationService as "Moderation\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Duyệt Tin Tuyển Dụng ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Duyệt nội dung"
FrontEnd -> ModerationService: GET /api/admin/jobs?status=PENDING&page=0&size=20
ModerationService -> Database: Query tin_tuyen_dung pending
Database --> ModerationService: Return list
ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Jobs list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị danh sách

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click vào tin
FrontEnd -> ModerationService: GET /api/admin/jobs/{jobId}
ModerationService -> Database: Get job details
Database --> ModerationService: Job info
ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Details
FrontEnd --> Admin: Xem chi tiết tin

Admin -> FrontEnd: Phê duyệt tin
FrontEnd -> ModerationService: POST /api/admin/jobs/{jobId}/approve
ModerationService -> Database: Update status = APPROVED
Database --> ModerationService: OK
ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Approved
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Phê duyệt thành công

Admin -> FrontEnd: Hoặc từ chối tin
FrontEnd -> ModerationService: POST /api/admin/jobs/{jobId}/reject\n(reason)
ModerationService -> Database: Update status = REJECTED
Database --> ModerationService: OK
ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Rejected
FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Từ chối thành công

== Duyệt Đơn Ứng Tuyển ==

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Đơn ứng tuyển"
FrontEnd -> ModerationService: GET /api/admin/applications?status=FLAGGED
ModerationService -> Database: Query don_ung_tuyen flagged
Database --> ModerationService: Return list
ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Applications list
FrontEnd --> Admin: Hiển thị danh sách

Admin -> FrontEnd: Click vào đơn
FrontEnd -> ModerationService: GET /api/admin/applications/{appId}
ModerationService -> Database: Get application details
Database --> ModerationService: Details
ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Full info
FrontEnd --> Admin: Xem chi tiết

if (Spam hoặc vi phạm?) then (Có)
  Admin -> FrontEnd: Click "Xóa nội dung"
  FrontEnd -> ModerationService: DELETE /api/admin/applications/{appId}
  ModerationService -> Database: Delete record
  Database --> ModerationService: OK
  ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Deleted
  FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Xóa thành công
else (Không)
  Admin -> FrontEnd: Clear flag
  FrontEnd -> ModerationService: PATCH /api/admin/applications/{appId}/clear-flag
  ModerationService -> Database: Update status
  Database --> ModerationService: OK
  ModerationService --> FrontEnd: Cleared
  FrontEnd --> Admin: ✅ Xóa cảnh báo thành công
endif

@enduml
